These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, sudoku
2 different games are played: poker, mah-jongg
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, western
City: liverpool, san-francisco
There are 2 different favourite colors: coral, blood-red
There 2 different types of food: zucchini, broccoli
1. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
3. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person who likes coral is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
6. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | fanta     | cola       |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | sudoku     |
| Game           | poker | mah-jongg   |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | superhero  |
| City   | san-francisco | liverpool |
| Color           | coral      | blood-red     |
| Food     | broccoli    | zucchini   |

