.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, golf
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, drawing
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, december
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, r&b
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, german
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, begonia
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, game
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is the game-smoker##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the fan of indie##1
4. the german is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Sport      | rowing    | golf |
| Hobby         | drawing        | dancing  |
| Birthday           | july | december  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b            | indie    |
| Nationality   | australian     | german   |
| Flower           | daffodil         | begonia    |
| Cigar     | bluemaster           | game      |

